{"tid":1733962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】維基百科戰爭：向國際求援","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T02:58:27.000Z","uid":89937,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5d3b9412289a877275b4886371a59cdb665e9d","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:22:54.000Z","msg":"由於小弟之前講得唔清楚，可能大家唔知點改，所以今次有圖教埋大家。（其他語言嘅就教大家巴打執生，但相信唔太難）<br />\n<br />\n1。除非條目被『半保護』或需要寫新條目，否則不一定註冊用戶才能修改。不一定註冊用戶才能修改。不一定註冊用戶才能修改。不一定註冊用戶才能修改。<br />\n<br />\n好重要所以講三次！<br />\n<br />\n2。第一步係去維基百科右上角嘅search engine搵到我哋要改嘅條目（或者喺其他Link Click入去），搵到之後按上面嘅『編輯』。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hefbJ8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhefbJ8b.png&h=c513f0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3。你可能會見到一大批Code，初學者可以去右邊有支筆嘅Logo Click入去，選擇視覺化編輯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZuoAfv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZuoAfv.png&h=6b2a8a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4。轉左去視覺化編輯之後，你可以好似平時用Word咁改野。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/18/162044_94ed809dd4b4c40b1be3630941c639a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F18%2F162044_94ed809dd4b4c40b1be3630941c639a9.png&h=ae34887d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab32374b1b7653f366f2e36af3c5afb98fe213c5","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"5。我哋需要有大量資料來源，否則容易被五毛指有關資料實為原創／不實，然後被提刪。但大家記得，千萬不要在這位置為紅媒（香港仔，文匯，大公，商報，點新聞、橙新聞）提供Hit Rate。<br />\n<br />\n大家寫完之後，可以喺嗰個句子最後加返消息來源，上面條Bar按『引用』，然後你會見到彈咗個Box出嚟，係下面貼返個網址。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C41uvRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC41uvRe.png&h=ed3a5f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6。之後按『產生』。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cVTD8C2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVTD8C2.png&h=73cf5c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7。記得按埋『插入』<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MSBaR5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MSBaR5.png&h=0a95f5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8。繼續進行其他修改，要Save就按『發佈變更』<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHZTc5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHZTc5u.png&h=d1446d3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f6b33868b6aea6b25bb97c231a22bef6da27e21","tid":1733962,"uid":267872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c85184986d90e900a5f7ca6d54df5f7a63e2506","tid":1733962,"uid":116275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:36:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e8eaa03b621bb6b5b94894888cd9e4a0acdd73ee","tid":1733962,"uid":116173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"咩方法都要試<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理大SOS</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另一方法：用人道理由施壓，堅持送食物、水同醫護人員入去！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1732806\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1732806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"93c9c4f34acc0f82802b7bf82f7156d8dee7dac9","tid":1733962,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"其實維基百科好需要市民幫手update，因為太多強國打手佔據抹黑。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245f56febbfb8b782c72dd53607b28af81c5b590","tid":1733962,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be8542f9ffb7e52ee216143130d4e4014d2dc00","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:03:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c4fa282e936a58822343e745ce30d6ed5f44d05","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a3d1c5c1d9f2f1b158bffcc30e65b20f702ce43","tid":1733962,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c9c4f34acc0f82802b7bf82f7156d8dee7dac9","tid":1733962,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"其實維基百科好需要市民幫手update，因為太多強國打手佔據抹黑。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"但香港人覺得唔可信，所以唔想貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015a6ee440a8b28d423d2bf378e6c2616acd4e9b","tid":1733962,"uid":204401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"推，但打英文係咪好啲"},{"pid":"d20260cdd6ce1de739df3022d5b87f1741b4d237","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015a6ee440a8b28d423d2bf378e6c2616acd4e9b","tid":1733962,"uid":204401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"推，但打英文係咪好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:36:56.000Z","msg":"打英文維基百科係好D<br />\n但相信呢度巴打會搞得掂"},{"pid":"65e1ab36c43dd1e2acfeb631bdfee869ae5fe68a","tid":1733962,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:53:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85586bd4ed30b8a66f1576281b3c8101abff4a8e","tid":1733962,"uid":173002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d20260cdd6ce1de739df3022d5b87f1741b4d237","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015a6ee440a8b28d423d2bf378e6c2616acd4e9b","tid":1733962,"uid":204401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"推，但打英文係咪好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:36:56.000Z","msg":"打英文維基百科係好D<br />\n但相信呢度巴打會搞得掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"英文版有其他國家管理員睇，<br />\n但中文版，香港就係散兵對大量有組織嘅強國打手，一邊粉飾暴政同CCTVB，一邊係所有反送中相關主題抹黑，<br />\n其實強國block左維基，強國人可以寫維基，九成以上係網軍，香港人想對就勢孤力弱，須要有多啲人註冊加入。"},{"pid":"76f82c671cdc9476f82bec499cc1e4439f54cf0a","tid":1733962,"uid":47200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nTwitter Reddit以外嘅網戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b0d69fa6f06182a3cc62211316715b3c6fe41f","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T21:42:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"126d6123e0f97754ac93a46eacdbece935faf061","tid":1733962,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T21:44:16.000Z","msg":"值得推不過推唔郁"},{"pid":"73a7ccc6823ade2066b6e1316fc057e39d5924ea","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"126d6123e0f97754ac93a46eacdbece935faf061","tid":1733962,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T21:44:16.000Z","msg":"值得推不過推唔郁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T22:16:23.000Z","msg":"你都註冊個戶口啦<br />\n依家原來好大獲<br />\n有人企圖o係維基百科封殺立場新聞同蘋果日報做資料來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1776851/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1776851/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"91a1ae6f4e47e08d0ee0843a4ce68d64ccea9ec1","tid":1733962,"uid":136916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T22:33:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"37afba8fe8e2bda2520059fbe095327d7fe7f427","tid":1733962,"uid":136916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T22:33:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4954ac0f6ebaa6f4210af53b34859d76cbd31d45","tid":1733962,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38501258d810859d6c35bdcfe8164cbfa8c08320","tid":1733962,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:57:51.000Z","msg":"大家星期日有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2be6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=537b62a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a6184ca9deec0fa441b5d20d711f09831e881917","tid":1733962,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}